<item>
            <title>[PIG-1458] aggregate files for replicated join</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1458</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have noticed that if the smaller data in replicated join has many files, this puts  unneeded burden on the name node. pre-aggregating the files can improve the situation&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12467278">PIG-1458</key>
            <summary>aggregate files for replicated join</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/issuetypes/improvement.png">Improvement</type>
